This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image restoration. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it proposes a new layer for neural networks. Additionally, it may belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with image processing, and the neural networks and learning (cs.NE) sub-category as it proposes a new layer for deep learning models.
